how to get basic blade of destiny : 
> up to level 50 character.
> collect rare item in 3 dungeon lev rare (glove, 1 thrones crsytal, book blade of destiny).
> get in dragon kingdom to finish mision.

how to get flame type the blade of destiny (just like before, some additional to get this) is : 
> before visit on the legendary dragon you must collect legendary item (feather of live) on dungon lev legendary
> you must visit on the legendary dragon in the dragon kingdom and finish that mision to get flame type the blade of destiny
